---
import Main from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Main title="Download" fullWidth={true}>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="download-hero">
		<div class="hero-bg">
			<div class="gradient-orb orb-1"></div>
			<div class="gradient-orb orb-2"></div>
			<div class="grid-overlay"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="hero-container">
			<div class="hero-content">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<span class="hero-badge">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
						Free & Open Source
					</span>
					<h1>
						Get Started with
						<span class="text-gradient-accent">R5Valkyrie</span>
					</h1>
					<p class="hero-description">
						Your all-in-one launcher for the ultimate Apex Legends modding experience. 
						Download games, manage mods, and join servers.
					</p>

					<div class="download-cta">
						<a
							href="https://github.com/r5valkyrie/launcher_releases/releases/latest"
							class="btn-download-main"
						>
							<span class="btn-icon">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
							</span>
							<span class="btn-text">
								<span class="btn-label">Download for Windows</span>
								<span class="btn-version">Windows 10/11 • 64-bit</span>
							</span>
							<span class="btn-arrow">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
							</span>
						</a>

						<div class="alt-downloads">
							<a href="https://github.com/r5valkyrie/launcher" target="_blank" class="alt-link">
								<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
								View Source Code
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="hero-visual">
					<div class="launcher-frame">
						<div class="frame-border"></div>
						<img src="/assets/launcher.jpeg" alt="R5Valkyrie Launcher Preview" />
						<div class="frame-reflection"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-1">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
							Auto Updates
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>The launcher automatically checks for updates and keeps your game files current. No manual patching required.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-2">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg>
							Mod Manager
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>Browse and install mods from Thunderstore with one click. Enable, disable, and organize your mod collection easily.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-3">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
							Server Browser
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>Custom in-game lobby browser to find community servers. See real-time player counts, ping, and game modes — join with a single click.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-4">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
							Patch Notes
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>View the latest patch notes and changelogs directly in the launcher. Stay informed about new features and fixes.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-5">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="4" y1="21" x2="4" y2="14"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="4" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="20" y1="21" x2="20" y2="16"/><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="20" y2="3"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="9" y1="8" x2="15" y2="8"/><line x1="17" y1="16" x2="23" y2="16"/></svg>
							Launch Options
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>Easy-to-use launch options interface. Configure graphics, performance settings, and custom parameters without editing files.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="floating-badge badge-6">
						<div class="badge-front">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/><path d="M16.72 11.06A10.94 10.94 0 0 1 19 12.55"/><path d="M5 12.55a10.94 10.94 0 0 1 5.17-2.39"/><path d="M10.71 5.05A16 16 0 0 1 22.58 9"/><path d="M1.42 9a15.91 15.91 0 0 1 4.7-2.88"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/></svg>
							Offline Mode
						</div>
						<div class="badge-info">
							<p>Play offline with bots or host local games without an internet connection. Perfect for practicing or LAN parties.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Features Section -->
	<section class="features-section">
		<div class="section-container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Everything You Need</h2>
				<p>One launcher to rule them all. Here's what's included.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="features-grid">
				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Game Downloader</h3>
					<p>Download and install the game directly from the launcher. No external tools needed.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon icon-accent">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><polyline points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96"/><line x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Mod Manager</h3>
					<p>Browse, install, and manage mods with a single click. Integrated Thunderstore support.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Server Browser</h3>
					<p>Custom in-game lobby browser to find and join community servers. See player counts, ping, and game modes.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon icon-accent">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Auto Updates</h3>
					<p>Stay up to date automatically. The launcher updates itself and notifies you of game updates.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Easy Configuration</h3>
					<p>Customize game settings, launch parameters, and more through an intuitive interface.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="feature-card">
					<div class="feature-icon icon-accent">
						<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
					</div>
					<h3>Community Driven</h3>
					<p>Built by the community, for the community. Open source and always improving.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Installation Steps -->
	<section class="install-section">
		<div class="section-container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Get Playing in Minutes</h2>
				<p>Three simple steps to join the action.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="steps-timeline">
				<div class="timeline-line"></div>
				
				<div class="step-card" data-step="1">
					<div class="step-marker">
						<span class="step-number">1</span>
						<div class="step-pulse"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<div class="step-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Download & Install</h3>
						<p>Click the download button above and run the installer. Follow the on-screen instructions to set up the R5Valkyrie Launcher on your system.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="step-card" data-step="2">
					<div class="step-marker">
						<span class="step-number">2</span>
						<div class="step-pulse"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<div class="step-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Download the Game</h3>
						<p>Open the launcher and click "Install" to download the game files. This may take a while depending on your connection speed.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="step-card" data-step="3">
					<div class="step-marker">
						<span class="step-number">3</span>
						<div class="step-pulse"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<div class="step-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"/></svg>
						</div>
						<h3>Play!</h3>
						<p>Hit the "Play" button and you're in! Browse servers, install mods, and customize your experience however you like.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- System Requirements -->
	<section class="requirements-section">
		<div class="section-container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>System Requirements</h2>
				<p>Make sure your system meets these specifications.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="requirements-grid">
				<div class="req-card">
					<div class="req-header">
						<span class="req-badge">Minimum</span>
						<p class="req-note">Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</p>
					</div>
					<ul class="req-list">
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">OS</span>
							<span class="req-value">Windows 10 64-bit</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">CPU (AMD)</span>
							<span class="req-value">FX 4350 or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">CPU (Intel)</span>
							<span class="req-value">Core i3 6300 or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">RAM</span>
							<span class="req-value">6 GB</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">GPU (AMD)</span>
							<span class="req-value">Radeon HD 7790 (2 GB) or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">GPU (NVIDIA)</span>
							<span class="req-value">GTX 950 or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">DirectX</span>
							<span class="req-value">Version 11</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">Network</span>
							<span class="req-value">Broadband Internet connection</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">Storage</span>
							<span class="req-value">75 GB available space</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="req-card req-recommended">
					<div class="req-header">
						<span class="req-badge badge-accent">Recommended</span>
						<p class="req-note">Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</p>
					</div>
					<ul class="req-list">
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">OS</span>
							<span class="req-value">Windows 10 64-bit</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">CPU (AMD)</span>
							<span class="req-value">Ryzen 5 or equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">CPU (Intel)</span>
							<span class="req-value">Core i5 6600K or equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">RAM</span>
							<span class="req-value">8 GB</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">GPU (AMD)</span>
							<span class="req-value">R9 290 or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">GPU (NVIDIA)</span>
							<span class="req-value">GTX 970 or Equivalent</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">DirectX</span>
							<span class="req-value">Version 11</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">Network</span>
							<span class="req-value">Broadband Internet connection</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="req-label">Storage</span>
							<span class="req-value">75 GB available space</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- FAQ Section -->
	<section class="faq-section">
		<div class="section-container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
				<p>Got questions? We've got answers.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-list">
				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>
						<span class="faq-question">Is R5Valkyrie free to use?</span>
						<span class="faq-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
						</span>
					</summary>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>Yes! R5Valkyrie is completely free and open source. There are no hidden fees, subscriptions, or paywalls. The entire project is community-driven and maintained by volunteers.</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>
						<span class="faq-question">Do I need to own Apex Legends?</span>
						<span class="faq-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
						</span>
					</summary>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>R5Valkyrie uses archived game files from older seasons that are no longer available through official channels. You don't need an active Apex Legends installation.</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>
						<span class="faq-question">Will I get banned from the official game?</span>
						<span class="faq-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
						</span>
					</summary>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>No. R5Valkyrie runs completely separately from the official game and uses different servers. We use Steam for authentication, but your EA/Origin account is never accessed or at risk.</p>
					</div>
				</details>

				<details class="faq-item">
					<summary>
						<span class="faq-question">How do I install mods?</span>
						<span class="faq-icon">
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
						</span>
